Class YaProjectEditor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProjectChangeListener, HasAttachHandlers, HasHandlers, EventListener, HasVisibility, IsRenderable, IsWidget

    public final class YaProjectEditor
extends ProjectEditor
implements ProjectChangeListener
    Project editor for Young Android projects. Each instance corresponds to one project that has been opened in this App Inventor session. Also responsible for managing screens list for this project in the DesignToolbar.
    Author:
    lizlooney@google.com (Liz Looney), sharon@google.com (Sharon Perl) - added logic for screens in DesignToolbar
